{"TopicId":209461,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"Strange camera shadow on bodies in map view","CreatedByName":"sweatbox","CreatedById":211503,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-22T00:49:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"sweatbox","CreatedById":211503,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-22T00:49:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey everyone, I\u0027m having a strange issue I can\u0027t figure out regarding there being a shadow on celestial bodies when zoomed in far enough in the map view. I\u0027ve provided a few screenshots to show what I mean and what it\u0027s supposed to look like.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nI am playing on a modded installation, however the issue doesn\u0027t appear to be caused by \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E or Spectra as I\u0027ve now removed those. I also have:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAVP\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nParallax\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nScatterer\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd several other mods that affect gameplay but not cosmetics. Has anyone experienced a similar issue before?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe issue while zoomed way in:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220220821153110_1.jpg?width=1618\u0026amp;height=9\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.75\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/494689411041198082/1011064390449102908/20220821153110_1.jpg?width=1618\u0026amp;height=910\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe issue while zoomed farther out:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220220821153106_1.jpg?width=1618\u0026amp;height=9\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.75\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/494689411041198082/1011064391099232326/20220821153106_1.jpg?width=1618\u0026amp;height=910\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow it\u0027s supposed to look:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220220821153112_1.jpg?width=1618\u0026amp;height=9\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.75\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/494689411041198082/1011064390746902599/20220821153112_1.jpg?width=1618\u0026amp;height=910\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-22T00:56:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224166376\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209461\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661129358\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211503\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sweatbox\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, sweatbox said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe issue while zoomed farther out:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you use TUFX?\u00A0 If so, try setting c\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#1c1c1c;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003Eonfig for map mode to default-empty. See if that clears it.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sweatbox","CreatedById":211503,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-22T01:11:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224166379\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209461\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661129788\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207619\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Caerfinon\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Caerfinon said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you use TUFX?\u00A0 If so, try setting c\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#1c1c1c;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003Eonfig for map mode to default-empty. See if that clears it.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do! I must have forgotten I had it installed - thanks for your response.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nI took a look in the config in-game and also poked around the files for the mod, but was unable to find the config you mentioned. I\u0027m sure I missed it somewhere; do you happen to know the path for this or if it\u0027s a setting in-game I can change?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks again!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: Nevermind! I found how to change the config. Thanks a lot for your help, it was really immersion breaking for me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-08-22T01:13:48Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2022 01:13  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by sweatbox\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-22T01:21:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224166382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209461\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221661130683\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211503\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sweatbox\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, sweatbox said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found how to change the config\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood to hear. Fly safe.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-22T05:24:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThread moved to modded support.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}